      "lat": "Ahum Khayrun 'Am Qawmu Tubba`in Wa Al-Ladhina Min Qablihim 'Ahlaknahum 'Innahum Kanu Mujrimina"
    },
    {
      "n": 38,
      "lat": "Wa Ma Khalaqna As-Samawati Wa Al-'Arđa Wa Ma Baynahuma La`ibina"
    },
